            <biogHist>
                <p>Margaret Campbell née Stewart was the daughter of Thomas Stewart, hawker, and
                    Elizabeth Stewart née Carmichael. She was married to Andrew Campbell, tinker and
                    hawker, and they had at least one daughter, Margaret Campbell. </p>
                <p>Margaret died of phthisis in 1939 and her daughter Margaret signed the death </p>
                <p>Carmichael collected tinker cant, a remedy for rheumatism and possibly a song
